title: LIVE From Bourbon & Beyond: NEEDTOBREATHE
itunes:title: LIVE From Bourbon & Beyond: NEEDTOBREATHE
description: Joining me on my backstage set at Bourbon & Beyond, Tyler Burkum, guitarist, and Josh Lovelace, Keyboardist  of NEEDTOBREATHE sip some super awesome bourbons with me: Old Fitzgerald Bottled in Bond 17 Year Spring 2022, Jack Daniel's 10 Year and Smoke Wagon 2 Hot for Retail. What great sipping companions!
